                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> Iu</supplied>noni <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Reg</abbr><ex>inae</ex></expan>? dis</supplied> deab<lb break="no" n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">usque</supplied> omnibus <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>o TOVTIO <lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>SIGIOPI <lb n="6"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>s Victo<lb break="no" n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">rinus mi</supplied><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VIII <lb n="8"/>[<expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <del rend="erasure"><supplied reason="lost">Ale</supplied>xandri</del>]<lb break="no" n="9"/><del rend="erasure">[anae</del>] b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>liano et <lb n="12"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ergänzung [Ae]liano et [Maximo] (Konsuln des Jahres 223) oder [Iu]liano et [Crispino] (Konsuln des Jahres 224) möglich. Nach Schallmayer et al. kommt dagegen nur (Lupo) Iu]liano et [Maximo] (Konsuln des Jahres 232) in Frage. Gefunden beim Abbruch der Kirche St. Kilian. Auf der rechten Nebenseite Baum. (B): AE 1978: Z. 2: Reg(inae) dis deab(usque); Schillinger-Häfele: dis deab(usque); Cubaynes: kleinere Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
